lead_paragraph: New Zealand's Danny Lee used a hot start to grab his first 54-hole lead in a PGA Tour event at the Waste Management Phoenix Open on Saturday while three-time winner Phil Mickelson vaulted into contention.

headline.print_headline: Lee Grabs Phoenix Open Lead, Mickelson Five Back
headline.main: Lee Grabs Phoenix Open Lead, Mickelson Five Back
